messages.msg: Welcome to our site! If you are looking for prayer or someone to chat with, reply to this message or email us at prayer@fightlust.com

I want lust broken off my soul I want the lust of the eyes and the lust of the flesh and the pride of life broken off my soul in the name of Jesus I want the mind of Christ to rule in my life and in my marriage I want all marriage breaking spirits broken off of my marriage and I pray for all marriages all across the world to be blessed and all marriages that are in shambles to be restored
